# Frontend Rules

<!-- NOTE: AGENTS.md is the master reference for project-wide rules.
     Keep rules here as a Cursor-specific subset. Don't add rules
     that contradict AGENTS.md. -->

- Prefer Server Components by default.
- Add `"use client"` only when interactivity is required.
- Use `pnpm` for all frontend package and script operations.
- Follow Next.js App Router conventions.
- Tailwind CSS v4 is configured via `postcss.config.mjs` and `globals.css`; do not introduce `tailwind.config.ts` unless explicitly requested.
- Prefer shadcn/ui components from `components/ui/` before creating custom primitives.
- Use `usePathname()` from `next/navigation` for active navigation state when needed.
- Keep components focused and composable.
- Use English in code, props, comments, and docs.